# Durable technical docs (ADRs, design decisions, troubleshoot reports)
# now live in the personal knowledge-base at
# ~/Source/Documents/knowledge-base/ — they are NOT tracked here. The
# directories themselves stay gitignored so a stray write under docs/
# in the project tree never leaks infra-shape info to the public repo.
docs/design-decisions/
docs/troubleshoot/
# auto-agents.nvim auto-injects a per-kind instruction file at the agent's
# cwd on every spawn (CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md / GEMINI.md). For *this* repo
# (the autovim config dir), don't track them — they're per-machine state.
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
GEMINI.md
data
vendor/
launch.json
.idea/
sample.com
.junie/

