# User-owned custom override layer (NvChad-style). The directory is
# gitignored so `git pull` / `update.sh` never touches user files.
# Starter templates live at docs/custom-example/ (tracked); the
# installer copies them into lua/custom/ on fresh install.
/lua/custom/
